basefwx (3.6.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging of the BaseFWX C++ codec library and CLI.
  * basefwx ships the command-line frontend; libbasefwx3 ships the runtime
    shared library; libbasefwx-dev ships headers, CMake config, and the
    pkg-config file.
  * Local builds can use the YUME vendor/linux-x86_64 liboqs staging area
    for ML-KEM-768. A Debian main upload must build against a separately
    packaged liboqs development package instead.

 -- FixCraft Maintainers <debian@fixcraft.jp>  Sat, 09 May 2026 22:00:00 -0700
